/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
25 October  2012	cnwrd1	Initial creation
01 December 2014    cnwma1  PAR #35314  1086 in MOB_HHLanderCargoMove::cmbSlotLocation_displayEntry
*/

